OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCitizens Advice: Millions  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Faffected by festive post   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdelays                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Millions of people missed important    
OL,6, post over Christmas due to             
OL,7, pandemic-related Royal Mail delays,    
OL,8, Citizens Advice has said.              
OL,10,FIt estimated that 2.5 million Royal    
OL,11,FMail customers missed documents such as
OL,12,Fhealth appointments, fines or bills.   
OL,14,FRoyal Mail said the wave of Omicron    
OL,15,Finfections meant that thousands of     
OL,16,Fstaff members had to take time off over
OL,17,FChristmas and January.                 
OL,19,FBut it said the "vast majority" of post
OL,20,Fwas delivered on time.                 
